properties.title: Swarm-EISCAT conjunction list (2013-2019)
properties.description: CSV file with a list of all conjunctions between Swarm A–C and either EISCAT-Svalbard or EISCAT-Tromsø Incoherent Scatter Radar. Conjunctions were identified by NASA’s «Satellite Situation Center Web» Query tool in August 2019.
